snippet.title: Medicine Of One
snippet.description: Medicine of One is a Non-dual path of freedom through the "True Action of Self-Love”: Shamanic Non-dualism; Invoking the Non dual big I to resolve the opposites, emotionally, mentally and physically. Clear the way to the quiet one. Join me in Sedona Arizona in the circle of grace: soul healing sessions, retreats, vision Quest, and soul journeys on the land.
